comments[4]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-07T09:44:04.849Z",codex-agent,"Integrator story update: pm-6abs adds hermetic package smoke-test diagnostics. A package author can run pm package doctor --project --isolated --detail deep --trace or isolate PM_GLOBAL_PATH for a whole test process; temp-dir dogfood proved a fresh package loaded only project:pm-temp-smoke."
  "2026-07-08T06:06:35.422Z",codex,"Evidence: package-consumer SDK proof now exercises the installed @unbrained/pm-cli SDK from a packed tarball in /tmp, covering init/create/update/claim/release/comments/notes/learnings/files/docs/deps/schema/profile/context/next/health/validate and returning ok with created item pm-yp8p and child pm-gps8."
  "2026-07-15T20:21:23.814Z",codex-root-20260715,"Implementation scope 2026-07-15: satisfy the SDK-only integrator story through the pm-cbwg executable exemplar and temp-installed acceptance flow; no private core imports are permitted."
  "2026-07-15T21:08:49.219Z",codex-root-20260715,"Acceptance evidence 2026-07-15: the SDK-only integrator story is executable rather than illustrative. A fresh consumer installs the packed pm distribution and runs the nested pm-sdk-tool binary without CLI implementation or private-core imports. The story exercises lifecycle, domain schema, ownership handoff, annotations, linked artifacts, bounded queries/context, relationship traversal, validation, and health before closure. Integration proof passes and the repository remains exact 100/100/100/100 coverage."
